				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Learned how to change the color of my Chat Ballon so thought I would share it with you.  I bound it to my Enter key so when I hit Enter to chat, it automatically puts in the things to change the colors.
<br />

<br />
You will type it exactly as I have it below.  You can use color names or the HTML version (#FF0000)
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">/bind Enter &quot;beginchat &lt;color yellow&gt;&lt;bgcolor red&gt;&lt;border blue&gt;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Has anyone come across a single key or command that turns Strafe on ala FPS type or like EQ?  For example, hold down CTRL key and then when you move left or right it strafes instead of turns.  I typically hit a Strafe with my thumb and use the arrow keys for Forward, Back, Left, Right.  Holding in the Right Mouse button gets annoying for me.
<br />

<br />
Any Binds or Macro's you want to share?<br />_________________<br /><table>
