My question is ... is there a Strafe Key or Command?  A is Strafe Left and D is Strafe Right.  That is fine but not what I want.  I want a "Strafe on" type key so that I hold that down and then Left arrow to Strafe Left or Right Arrow to Strafe right.  That way, I can use the Arrow keys to Move Forward, Move Back, Turn Left, Turn Right, CTRL Left to Strafe Left, CTRL Right to Strafe Right.
<br />

<br />
I guess I swap between movement modes a lot.  I don't exclusively use the WASD construct with the mouse.  I would rather use the Arrow Keys to move and the keyboard for targetting and other functions.
<br />

<br />
I suppose I could bind some abilities to some mouse buttons to do some of the keyboard functions now that I think about it...or actually start using that Nostromo n52 I bought heh<br />_________________<br /><table>
