<br />

<br />
I havent gotten into binds much yet, but something like this should work:   /bind rcontrol+larrow "[+left]"
<br />

<br />
Theres not much of a comprehensive list for commands and key names avail yet though, so Im not sure if larrow is correct. (it is rcontrol though)...
