				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I made a macro today for tps so people stop falling off buildings when i tp them while they are running hehe
<br />
example:
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">/macro TP &quot;say Teleporting $target to me -hold still $$ powexec_name recall friend&quot;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
generic:
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">/macro &lt;hotkey name&gt; &quot;say &lt;message&gt; $$ powexec_name &lt;power name&gt;&quot;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
$target = %t
