<br />

<br />
Vestrial</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
It's most efficient if you become proficient using it <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="icon_razz.gif" border="0" />  The problem I have is that when I move my fingers from WASD to cast spells, I waste time getting them back in place to move properly and sometimes miss the placement and end up moving the wrong way <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="icon_razz.gif" border="0" />  At least in most FPS I can use the Mouse to shoot and the wheel to swap weapons and whatnot so I rarely have to move the left hand from the WASD keys.  
<br />

<br />
I tried using the NumPad to cast spells but it wasn't working for me at that point (Guess I have to go into Options and set up Alt Keybindings to do that).
<br />

<br />
See, if I can map a Strafe to the CTRL key, I won't really need to use the mouse much at all and can keep one hand on movement keys and use the other for keyboard commands.<br />_________________<br /><table>
